<main class="w-11/12 flex-1 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto bg-white mt-24 pb-24 md:px-8 xl:px-0" id="contents">
	<div class="text-center w-full px-4 bg-white md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2 mx-auto" id="input">
		<h1 class="font-black mb-4 text-2xl">電話番号認証</h1>
		<div class="text-left mb-8">
			<div class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">
				<p>本人確認のため、携帯電話のSMS（ショートメッセージサービス）を利用して認証を行います。電話番号が他のお客さまに公開されることはありません。</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<%= form_with, url: verification_user_mobile_phone_path do |f| %>
			<%= render partial: "shared/error_messages", locals: {resource: @user_mobile_phone } %>
			<div class="text-left">
				<div class="mb-8">
					<%= f.label :auth_code, class: "block text-grey-500 text-sm font-bold mb-2" %>
					<%= f.text_field :auth_code, class: "appearance-none border border-gray-300 rounded py-2 px-3 text-grey-darker w-full",placeholder: "1234"%>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div>
				<div class="text-center mb-2 flex flex-col space-y-4">
					<%= f.submit "次へ", class: "text-base font-bold bg-red-500 text-white p-2 w-full block py-4 rounded-sm" %>
				</div>
			</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</main>